ygData.subject: Re: Level 8 - 9 soloing
ygData.msgSnippet: Well, I found soloing at those lvls very tough.  But if you must solo, and your in the freeport area, try soloing in ecommons, there should be some things
ygData.messageBody:
Well, I found soloing at those lvls very tough. But if you must solo, and
your in the freeport area, try soloing in ecommons, there should be some
things there for you. Watch out for the Kodiaks, lions, and griffins
though.

Tandayen, Dark Elf Wizard
